{
  "stem": "21786.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--telling us about how the prisoners were being transported on a train towards Theresien.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There we got stuck on this train station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there many of my fellow prisoners died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was raining, so as it was difficult to sit on the floor of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were full of water, so we sat on our poor dead fellow prisoners, who didn't mind at that point.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that point, they let us bury some of our dead comrades.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a fight between the SS and the railway employees, who insisted that they will give us our-- their ration, their food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the first time after two days when we got some food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Water was-- that wasn't bad for it was raining.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the food, that was tough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we got something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we are seeing the tracks-- the trains with the wounded German soldiers trekking back towards Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were stuck for two days standing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And suddenly, on the night between 8 and 9 of May, we didn't realize that this-- 7 and 8 of May, sorry-- that the war came to an end.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They hitched an engine to us, and they dragged us to something called Litomarice, L-I-T-O-M-A-R-I-C-E, which was a-- we were stopped there on a train station.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from there, it was still, blackout.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was in the darkness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the distance we have seen a lit huge space, a city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We knew it's Theresien.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Theresien was lit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Something very unusual.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we got the order to get out of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "No beating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the-- the whip was a short guy who was standing on a box and was telling us that if we marched orderly-- that it's night.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
